# {{US}} At its most [[arrogant]], the [[political]] [[doctrine]] that The [[United States of America]] is destined to rule the world in a mild, understanding, [[inherently]] [[Christian]] way: all you have you to do is become us. The less arrogant version is that we support your ethnic, linguistic, religious and cultural ways, but insist you minimally behave like we do: respectful of government, law, and religion, and never doing a [[breech of the peace]].